         <abstract id="aspace_015448b6f1adf1a244d5ce8b96eb1e05">This collection consists of textiles, commemorative objects, and publications documenting African response to the election of Barack Obama as President of the United States in 2008.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_7060bd52adf9e77602f916d7f0df4797">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>Transferred from the African Collection Curator, 2013.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_4f62f3ba06045cb7d8563eb7964b6739">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection consists of textiles, commemorative objects, and publications documenting African response to the election of Barack Obama as President of the United States in 2008.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_7ac7cedad5d80f0147ddce2fec77040f">
